{
  "stem": "3165.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And then this lady said, and they took her away, and they gave her over to the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So now my sister and I, [SOBS] the two of us just left alone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I-- I just couldn't believe it that my mother is gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Is no more with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were two young children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it was just-- I-- I-- I just didn't know what we're going to do now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And now the lady tells us again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "She says, you know, you kids can't stay here, because they'll find you, and they'll take you away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And you've got to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So now Susan and I, the two of us, had to leave that house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Now I had to start looking for a place where to hide.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it's winter now, and we're hungry, and we're cold [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and all alone and mustn't say you're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And running and running again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And, you know, my mother was running to look for place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Now I started to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we'd find a house, which they would keep us for a day or two.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And again, they'd say, you know, you've gotta go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "You can't stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And this was going on and on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Find-- find a house to sleep over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] then one night, I went to look again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And I would leave my sister now, and I'd go look for a place, and then I'd find it and come back and say, OK, we've got to move now to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And then one night, I went into this village-- to this house, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
